G90 ; Set Absolute Positioning
G21 ; Set Units to Millimeters
G0 Z8.00 ; Lift to general safe height
; --- Start Dip Cycle ---
G0 Z10.00 ; Lift brush to higher safe height before dipping move
G0 X51.00 Y3.00 ; Move to wipe location center (before wipe/shake)
G0 Z6.00 ; Lift brush to intermediate Z for wipe travel
G1 X61.00 Y3.00 Z6.00 F1200 ; Move to start of wipe circle at wipe Z
G2 X61.00 Y3.00 I-10.00 J0.00 F1200 ; Perform circular wipe
G1 X51.00 Y3.00 Z6.00 F1200 ; Return to center after circular wipe
G0 Z10.00 ; Lift brush to z_safe_dip after wipe/shake
G0 X51.00 Y3.00 ; Return to dip center after wipe/shake (at z_safe_dip)
; --- End Dip Cycle ---
G0 X13.47 Y25.00 Z8.00 ; Move to start of stroke (at Z_safe)
G1 Z4.17 F600.0 ; Lower brush to start painting Z
